    dc:creator "Shi, Ai-Min; Yuan, Shi-Bin; Wu, Chun-Lian" ;
    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "Three new species of Itagonia Reitter, 1887 (Coleoptera, Tenebrionidae: Blaptini) from Sichuan, China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197441>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197442>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197443>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197444> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197441>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 10. Apical part of profemur. 1. I. provostii (Fairmaire); 2. I. semenowi Reitter; 3. I. zayica Shi & Ren; 4. I. baxoica Liu & Ren; 5. I. shamaevi Medvedev; 6. I. longicornis Shi & Ren; 7. I. trisetosa Medvedev; 8. I. mera Medvedev; 9. I. elegans Medvedev; 10. I. cordiformis Shi & Ren. (Fig. 1 from Egorov, 2007; Fig. 2 from Ren & Yu, 1999; Fig. 4 from Liu & Ren, 2009; Fig. 5 from Medvedev, 2004; Figs 7 – 9 from Medvedev, 1998)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197441/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197442>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 23. Itagonia tuberculata, sp. nov. 11. antenna of male; 12. antenna of female; 13. pronotum of male; 14. profemur and protibiae of male; 15. mesofemur and mesotibiae of male; 16 – 17. apical part of aedeagus in dorsal and ventral views; 18. aedeagus in lateral view; 19. spiculum gastrale; 20. abdominal inner sternite 8 of male; 21 – 22. ovipositor in dorsal and ventral views; 23. spiculum ventrale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197442/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197443>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24 – 36. Itagonia xinlongensis, sp. nov. 24. antenna of male; 25. antenna of female; 26. pronotum of male; 27. profemur and protibiae of male; 28. mesofemur and mesotibiae of male; 29 – 30. apical part of aedeagus in dorsal and ventral views; 31. aedeagus in lateral view; 32. spiculum gastrale; 33. abdominal inner sternite 8 of male; 34 – 35. ovipositor in dorsal and ventral views; 36. spiculum ventrale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197443/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197444>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37 – 49. Itagonia medvedevi, sp. nov. 37. antenna of male; 38. antenna of female; 39. pronotum of male; 40. profemur and protibiae of male; 41. mesofemur and mesotibiae of male; 42 – 43. apical part of aedeagus in dorsal and ventral views; 44. aedeagus in lateral view; 45. spiculum gastrale; 46. abdominal inner sternite 8 of male; 47 – 48. ovipositor in dorsal and ventral views; 49. spiculum ventrale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197444/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

